* {{homophones|en|air|Ayr|ere|eyre|heir}}, [[err]] {{qualifier|one pronunciation}}; [[e'er]]

====Noun====
{{en-noun}}

# {{senseid|en|unit of area}} {{lb|en|rare}} An accepted (but [[deprecate]]d and rarely used) [[metric]] unit of area equal to 100 [[square metre]]s, or a former unit of approximately the same extent. ''Symbol'': '''[[a]]'''.

=====Usage notes=====
* '''Are''' is now rarely used except in its derivative {{m|en|hectare}}.

=====Synonyms=====
* {{sense|SI unit}} {{qualifier|rare}} square [[decametre]]

